The '''Arizona Heat''' is a women's softball team based in [[Tucson, Arizona]]. From the 2004 season, it played as a member of [[National Pro Fastpitch]]. The team's home games were played at historic [[Hi Corbett Field]]. 

Six of the players on the 2006 roster played college softball at the [[University of Arizona#Softball|University of Arizona]], and two more played for [[Arizona State University]].

The team was suspended in February 2007.<ref>http://www.azstarnet.com/sn/related/168670</ref>

==Notable players==
*Shana Easley- CATCHER
*Catalina Morris - OUT FIELD
*Nichole Thompson - INNER FIELD
*Jessica Mendoza - PITCHER

